&lt;p&gt;As team leader you will be responsible for managing the delivery of a high quality service working with service users and staff to ensure practices that respond effectively to both individual and service need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will provide effective clinical leadership to ensure all nursing staff receives the appropriate supervision and support in conjunction with an agreed professional development plan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Furthermore, the post holder will be responsible for establishing and maintaining team systems and processes for effective operation of the team, including managing the shift patterns, outcome measurements, audit and annual service policy review.&lt;/p&gt;
